data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This immaculate, move-in ready gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, and 2 spacious living areas with a charming chimney creating the perfect blend of comfort and style. Located in a well-established neighborhood! Picture yourself enjoying morning coffee on the back porch or gathering with your friends and family in the generous backyard.   Don't miss your chance to call this house your home! Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm.!
